    <h1>ValueCam Support</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">We're here to help. Find answers below or reach out directly.</p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <dl class="faq">
        <dt>How does ValueCam work?</dt>
        <dd>Take a photo of any object and our AI instantly analyzes it to estimate its market value based on real marketplace data.</dd>

        <dt>Is ValueCam free?</dt>
        <dd>Yes! ValueCam is completely free to use with unlimited scans.</dd>

        <dt>How accurate are the valuations?</dt>
        <dd>Valuations are AI-generated estimates based on current market data. They provide a helpful range but should not be considered professional appraisals.</dd>

        <dt>Why does the app need my location?</dt>
        <dd>Location is used to provide region-specific pricing and display values in your local currency. You can deny location access and the app will still work.</dd>

        <dt>Why does the app need camera access?</dt>
        <dd>The camera is used to photograph items for valuation. You can also pick existing photos from your gallery instead.</dd>

        <dt>Is my data stored anywhere?</dt>
        <dd>No. Photos are processed in real time and are not stored on any server. All app data is stored locally on your device.</dd>

        <dt>How do I delete my data?</dt>
        <dd>Simply uninstall the app. All data is stored on your device only.</dd>
    </dl>

